<p><strong>Social Event Planning</strong> <br />
Core skills: gathertown (for the online component) <br />
Dates: 01/05 - 01/06 <br />
Time commitment: 1-2 hours  <br /></p>

<p><ins>Tasks</ins></p>
<ul>
